="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-54_">機能性的極致發揮，還原最根本的穿著體驗</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-55_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-56_ pf-sm-hide"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-57_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/2e6a2517-1646813407012_1200x.jpg?v=1646813424" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/2e6a2517-1646813407012.jpg?v=1646813424 1536w" width="5800" height="3867" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-58_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-59_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-60_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-62_">町田佳廣（Yoshihiro Machida）給予「和紙T」極高的機能性評價。<br><br>和紙T在纖維裡，保存了木組織的多孔性質，機制與木炭類似，具有許多細小的氣孔，並有大量微生物在這些氣孔中生存，能夠吸收水分、汙染物、細菌、氣味甚至紫外線；因此，除了透氣性，也有非常優異的抗菌和除臭效果，可謂不折不扣的除臭和紙衣、抗菌衣物，特別適合潮濕、溫熱氣候的國家客戶穿著。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-63_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-64_ pf-sm-hide"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-65_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/2e6a2546-1647852101886_1200x.jpg?v=1647852110" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/2e6a2546-1647852101886.jpg?v=1647852110 1536w" width="5193" height="3462" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-66_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-67_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-68_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-70_">町田佳廣（Yoshihiro Machida）也提到他在長跑後會有水泡的困擾，以及鞋內潮濕悶熱而感到不適，但他在穿過由和紙布製成的五指襪後表示：「一開始穿上感覺有點硬，類似在沙地上行走。但即使連續跑步幾天，也不會出現水泡。」<br><br>由此可見，和紙材質的服飾，越是使用，越能達到親膚效果，還原最原始的穿著體驗，宛如第二層肌膚穿著感受。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-72_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cbTzjv cciAhs pf-73_"></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-74_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-75_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-76_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-78_">環保新潮流，和紙衣的回溫</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-79_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-80_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-81_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-83_">PROJEXT 的設計團隊在如今步調緊湊的服飾業大環境中，依舊為了環境而努力、為了文化而傳承，選擇了重拾經典工藝的溫潤，讓這項被聯合國教科文組織認定為世界文化遺產的和紙，再現於服飾材質，成為件件精工製成的和紙衣。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-84_ pf-r pf-r-eh pf-sm-hide" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-85_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-86_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/m_papier_white_3-1-1647942740711_1200x.jp